## **5. Modifications to the Service and Terms**
- The bot owner reserves the right to modify or discontinue Synex at any time without prior notice.
- The owner may also update these Terms of Service from time to time. Continued use of Synex after such changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.

## **6. Governing Law**
- These terms shall be governed by and interpreted in accordance with the laws of the jurisdiction in which the bot owner resides.

